Package algorithms

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    advence_dijkstra
    the class advence_dijkstra is responsible to find the shortest route from one global point to another. while take care not crash into the boxes this class works basing on the dijkstra algorithm
    advence_dijkstra_node
    the class represent a dijkstra node it implements Comparable in in order to sort the nodes by theirdistance
    closet_fruit
    the class use advence_dijkstra in order to find the closet fruit to the player and the route to this fruit
    cross
    this class is responsible to check if a straight line between 2 global points is cross one box at list.
    deal_with_fruit
    this class is responsible to take care of the case that during the movement of the player, he pass close to a fruit. so the algorithm in this class cause him to go to the close fruit and then continue with his regular path.
    deal_with_ghost
    the class responsible on the case when during the movement of the player he pass close to a ghost and the are going to crash. so the class make it not happen
    deal_with_pachman
    this class is responsible to take care of the case that during the movement of the player, he pass close to a pachman. so the algorithm in this class cause him to go to the close pachman and then continue with his regular path.
    fruit_group
    this class represent a group of fruit
    fruit_group_layer
    this class represent group of groups of fruits The class responsibility is to divide the fruits into groups by their distance from each other (without consider the boxes).
    starting_point
    this class is responsible to determine witch point will be the starting point of the player
